    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 requirements for a Class II device with medium model influence. The hemolysis model form is supported by a systematic literature review of 17 peer-reviewed publications. Predicted RH values are below the acceptance threshold of 1.0 across all five operating points. The credibility body of evidence is deemed sufficient to support the regulatory submission claim.",
